  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promoting the peaceful coexistence of farmers and pastoralists</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Both sedentary farmers and pastoralists in Niger must be self-sufficient and able to earn a steady income. To make this goal a reality, the SDC has been involved in the &amp;quot,Programme d&#x2019;appui au secteur de l&#x2019;&#xE9;l&#xE9;vage&amp;quot, (PASEL, livestock farming support programme) since 1998. Together with local partners, it promotes the peaceful coexistence of farmers and pastoralists. In the past, conflicts of interests led to sometimes violent confrontations.</narrative>
  </description>
